markets.title: One Battle After Another Rotten Tomatoes score?
markets.subtitle: Above 97
markets.rules_primary: If One Battle After Another has a Tomatometer score of above 97 on Sep 29, 2025 at 10:00 AM ET, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: The "Fresh!" and "Certified Fresh!" subtitles are meant for illustrative purposes only. The Tomatometer score must be above the strike value to resolve as YES (for example, a score of 75 would resolve "Above 75" as No.) The market will be determined the Monday after wide release at 10:00 AM ET.
